        "@value": "Register of Auditors and Sub-’s of Audit Activity"
      },
      "dct:description": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The data set contains information from “Register of Auditors and ʼ Sub-Audit Entities. There are two resources in the dataset: subjects - information about ʼ subjects of audit activities and auditors - information about auditors. Access to the registry is also possible through a public web interface on the official website of OSNAD, at the link: https://register.apob.org.ua/uk/search"
      },
